  ‚ü®fun h => fun _s _t hs ht => h.indepSet_of_measurableSet hs ht, fun h s t hs ht =>
    h s t hs ht s t (measurableSet_generateFrom (Set.mem_singleton s))
      (measurableSet_generateFrom (Set.mem_singleton t))‚ü©

